text.section:
Each person who offers a program of continuing pharmaceutical education shall:
Provide a means for registration by the participants;
Maintain a record of participation for at least 3 years; and
Furnish each participant with adequate documentation of satisfactory completion of the program, including:
The name of the participant;
The name of the sponsor;
The type of program completed;
The number of continuing education hours or units completed; and
The date of completion.
